			<span class="btn-link"  href=""><li id="sharingfaq">Why is sharing with some applications not working?</li></span>
			<div class="collapse" id="question5">
				<ol>
				<li>This issue arises if your website is not publicly hosted. Facebook, for example looks for the URL to generate its preview for sharing. That does not work on localhost or any privately hosted URL.</li>
				</ol><br>
				For any further queries, please submit a query on right hand side in our <b>Support Section</b>.
